<h1>Shipping & Return</h1>

<p>ALL ORDERS SHIP FROM TOKYO, JAPAN</p>

<p>We aim to process and send your order within 2-4 working days. Orders placed on weekend will be processed from Monday.</p>

<p>We select Japan Post which offers the best international delivery service for you.</p>

<p>Orders over USD 59 are automatically sent by Express Mail Service (EMS). EMS offers tracked air delivery and full insurance coverage of your package as the value declared. Orders usually arrive at your door within 2-7 days.  We will notice you to your PayPal registered mailing address enclosing the tracking number of package.</p>

<p>For Orders under USD 59, please feel free to select EMS or International ePacket which you think is best for you. Please note that International ePacket type delivery usually takes 7-15 days and offers limited insurance up to USD 6000.</p>

<p>Large orders may be sent as one large package or split into smaller parcels. For orders of over 10 of the specific variations/ products, please contact us personally through our contact form.</p>

<h2>Customs duty and import taxes</h2>

<p>We cannot be held responsible for any import tax/customs duties as this will depend on the destination country.  The value of your order will be stated on your package due to customs authorities’ requirement.</p>

<h2>Shipping cost</h2>

<h3>EMS</h3>

<p>Tracked Air Delivery, insurance fully coverage</p>

<ul>
  <li>Asia Zone starts from USD 10</li>
  <li>US /Australia Zone starts from USD 12</li>
