The shipping costs are indicated at the checkout and are based on the weight of items you order.

<h2>Payment</h2>

<p>All credit card transactions are securely processed by PayPal. It is not necessary to register a PayPal account in order to make a payment.</p>

<h2>Return</h2>

<p>Please choose your purchase carefully as all deals are final. Due to the hygiene reasons, no return or exchanges are accepted on any product unless proven faulty.</p>

<p>Please contact us immediately in following circumstances:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Damaged items</p>
    <p>If the product is damaged and unusable, please keep the box as well as products and contact us within 3 days when you receive the package, enclosing and picture of the damaged products and your invoice number.  Please note that if only the box is damaged but items remained intact, the insurance doesn’t cover.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Lost items</p>
    <p>Please contact us immediately if you believe your package has been lost, so we can track the package and file an insurance claim.</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>For more information on approximate days required for EMS delivery check <%- utils.link_to('http://www.post.japanpost.jp/int/deli_days/ems/tokai_en.html', 'the Japan Post website') %>.</p>

<p>Note, in rare occasions custom agents may delay delivery of some packages. Please contact your local customs office first before claiming lost package.</p>

<h2>Faulty delivery</h2>

<p>If the goods you have received are faulty which are different from your original order, this must contact us within 5 days. Please don’t test the product before you send it back to us with tracking delivery. We will send your correct order soon after we received the package. Your return shipping cost will be refunded or you can choose another product with an equal value.</p>

<h2>Out of stock</h2>

<p>If the goods you order are currently out of stock or discontinued as limited/seasonal collection, we will notice you as soon as possible after your order are placed. Your purchase will be refunded or you can choose another substitute product.</p>

<h2>Pre-Order</h2>

<p>For limited/seasonal collection, we recommend you to place the pre-order. We will process your order and send to you within 2 working days as soon as when the goods are officially released for sale.</p>
